hopobject.body:
LCD cape for beaglebone / beaglebone black with capacitive touchscreen.

The LCD is 5" 800x480 from Newhaven Display.

24 bit true color.

Multitouch capacitive touch screen.

4 user buttons.

Header for adafruit adxl335 accelerometer (not included, supported by Kernel).

Ubuntu with Kernel 3.8 (device tree) support.

Rowboat android with Kernel 3.2 support.
